Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura turned out to be the one who got my stolen God Cards back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he said that an "Ultimate Dark Game" existed in my Lost Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura, I may not know what you're up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now we're finally here in Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's finally time to open the door to my Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Door of Memory Opens"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally got here! Egypt sure is really far!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, just hold on for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Anzu, you can buy souvenirs later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is it! I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, we're not here for sightseeing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0}! Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you all been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes we are. You guys look as energetic as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We came all the way to Egypt with tons of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will guide you to where the stone palette resides.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. And sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're {\i1}huge{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are real pyramids, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that! It's the Sphinx!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Ah, it really {\i1}is{\i0} missing its nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The stone tablet that unlocks the door to my memories lies inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the three cards are placed on the Memory Tablet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the door to your lost memories opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh, from this point onwards, you'll choose your own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we'll move on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, with this, our mission is accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate that our family of Tomb Guardians have borne for three thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every soul has its own place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh has now started on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's finally time for the door to the Nameless Pharaoh's memories to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Memory Tablet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I called him "Yugi" like always...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he's in Yugi's body,\N he's a completely {\i0}different{\i1} person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't even know his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Cartouche pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ancient Pharaohs always had their names written on them, I hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no name engraved on this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you regain your memories and remember your {\i1}real{\i0} name...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll carve it on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll never forget it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The portion on that palette with the Pharaoh's name got worn off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I want to know your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's is a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you engrave your name on it, you'll never forget your name again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treasure it always!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm back here again... with the three God Cards in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will happen from here on out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The start line has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clone of myself I left within the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has given the gong announcing the start of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is... the door to my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At long last, the time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a sudden burst of bright light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean he's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not in the Puzzle or in my heart anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh's soul has left the host.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh has embarked on a journey to the Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...! Shadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You were the one back at Battle Ship..!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me and Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also a Millennium Item wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh! Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on..?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, the people are waiting for your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give them a response.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... the Pharaoh....?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh! Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at the ceremony are also waiting for the new Pharaoh to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, here, to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Memory World?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, raise your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new Pharaoh has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ji-Jii"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Shimon, is the Pharaoh perhaps a bit fatigued?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm fine. Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, continue the music and dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show the vitality and strength of the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's happening? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are... the Millennium Items...! They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not because they are the six High Priests chosen by the Millennium Items?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The six High Priests chosen by the Millennium Items?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy's passed out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bad luck. There's a big feast being held in the main hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the days for a graverobbing, he decided to pick the day the new Pharaoh got crowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I'd start off looking like {\i1}this{\i0} after finally getting the game started...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no doubting it.\N This is in his Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This must mean you've came here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm slowly recalling all the small details from three thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's the Pharaoh...\N and I'm only a lowly bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difference in our rankings is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's looks a lot like Grandpa Sugoroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ishizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could the reason Grandpa Sugoroku found the Millennium Puzzle be because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the fact Ishizu comes from a family of Tomb Guardians...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe they weren't just mere coincidences?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the priest that is also carved on the Memory Tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insolent scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To aim for the Pharaoh's life...\N What a terrible act to commit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we are amidst celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the dungeons with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a good chance for us to show our powers to the new Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree,\N Sir Akhenaden? Sir Shimon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That is a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall punish this man in the presence of the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall hereby start the Repentance Ceremony for this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repentance Ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our new Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Egypt has now become a big country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But along with that comes bad people who are jealous of our success.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But rest assured, Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as us six High Priests are around, nobody will lay even a finger upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now your crime will be judged by the seven Millennium Items!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're using the Millennium Items to judge people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Priest Shada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the power of the Millennium Anhk, I look into this man's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the shadow of an evil abrasion residing in this man's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To reveal the true form of that abrasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, High Priest Akhenaden,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will use the power of the Millennium Eye to expose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, I believe this is your first time seeing the extraction of {\i1}Ka{\i0} from a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ka{\i0} comes about from the anger and hatred residing in people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ka{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...these evil {\i1}Ka{\i0} make these people commit crimes to increase their anger and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The priests chosen by the power of one thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have the power to exorcise these {\i1}Ka{\i0} and seal them within stone slabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stone slabs...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Priest Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the power of your Millennium Rod to {\i1}seal{\i0} the {\i1}Ka{\i0} within the stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}Ka{\i0} of this low level \Nisn't even an {\i1}amusement{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil {\i1}Ka{\i0}, dark spirit of chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone and enter the holy stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This... is the true power of the Millennium Items..!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Host for the soul of the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soul of the Pharaoh no longer exists within your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh has embarked on a journey into his Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memory World?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Memory World is a place the Pharaoh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,created based on his experiences three thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he forgotten about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should still have his present memories even when he's in his Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Pharaoh is experiencing his fate once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the mystery as to why the Pharaoh's soul was sealed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Millennium Puzzle will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soul of the other Yugi will be sealed in the Millennium Puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, won't that mean that the other Yugi will never come back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My physical body has already been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... are talking to a ghost..?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My physical body was killed\N by Bakura's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirit residing in Bakura's body is that of a very evil person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, the nameless Pharaoh will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These Millennium Items told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That in order to know the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the nameless Pharaoh and Dark Bakura have traveled to the Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with the Dark Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, the two of them will start the Ultimate Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why would he not tell us such an important thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Yugi probably didn't want us to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can't I be of any help to the other me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know something, or else you wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help the other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is indeed a way to send you all to the Pharaoh's Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The labyrinth of the Pharaoh's heart that exists within the Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must find the Door of Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maze of his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh's Memory World lies behind that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I look a bit kingly {\i1}myself{\i0}, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to bring you to Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be {\i1}overjoyed{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's give our greetings to the Pharaoh, you scoundrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. I'm sure it was {\i1}dull{\i0} for the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we {\i1}draw and quarter{\i0} this prisoner for his amusement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evil abrasion in that man's spirit has been completely removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of our duties as priests is to show {\i1}mercy{\i0} to sinful criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:20:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado, supervision of security within this city is the duty of {\i1}your{\i0} guards, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the royal tombs are being defiled {\i1}too often{\i0} these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take responsibility for not doing the job well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, for the last few days
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the auguries I receive from the Millennium Ring have been extremely erratic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evil intents of the criminals are unfathomable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beseech you to allow an increase in the number of guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Er, yes. I leave it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the newly sealed {\i1}Ka{\i0} Tablet to the Shrine of Wedju!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't understand a single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this really the Ultimate Dark Game that Bakura was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not worry, great Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Shimon, have taken {\i1}personal{\i0} responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to design the tomb where you will have your eternal rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My tomb...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've placed numerous traps in the tomb and no bandits will be able to break in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After {\i1}your{\i0} death, Pharaoh, I {\i1}guarantee{\i0} you will rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Everyone, please continue the celebrations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Isis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Millennium Tauk foretells a disturbing future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A disturbing future?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An evil shadow approaches this palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with incredible powers of {\i1}Heka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this started...\N the Ultimate Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Yugi has finally arrived in his Lost Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were told that he needs to experience the fate he went through three thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Dark Personality Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} is there with him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't know about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duel with Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} in the Memory World begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rush to your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter the Thief King, Bakura!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.32,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
